  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf - \u0baa\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka's recent situation is a warning for the Asia-Pacific region",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Recent developments in Sri Lanka highlight the threat of social and labor unrest in the Asia-Pacific region due to the impact of the rising cost of living, according to S&P Global Market Intelligence.",
        "S&P Global Market Intelligence, a global business and financial evaluation company, is based in New York, USA.",
        "The agency pointed out that many countries like Sri Lanka are facing political and social unrest as a result of weak economic fundamentals, poor economic policies, the spread of the coronavirus, the Russia-Ukraine conflict, external influences such as increased fuel prices, and inflation.",
        "Apart from that, especially countries like Pakistan, Nepal, Bangladesh and Laos are facing a crisis similar to Sri Lanka, S&P Global Market Intelligence has stated."
      ],
